    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this wonderful find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a smooth and dependable driving experience you can truly rely on. It\u2019s a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a solid, quality ride that's ready for its next adventure!",
